# Backend — FastAPI

## Stack

- FastAPI + Pydantic v2 + SQLAlchemy 2.0
- Align REST paths with `prd.md` §14 (`/auth`, `/farms`, `/sensor-readings`, `/predict/irrigation`, etc.)

## Security

- Users may only access their own farms and related data.
- Passwords must be hashed; never store plaintext.
- Protect mutating endpoints with auth.

## Data

- Sensor readings require `source_type` enum: `manual | simulation | test_dataset`.
- Validate ranges before persisting (moisture 0–100, pH 0–14, etc.).
- Rainfall probability lives on `SensorReadings` — no separate Weather table in MVP.

## Errors

- Return meaningful Turkish error messages and correct HTTP status codes.
